---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy & Data - XAOSTECH" description="XAOSTECH Privacy Policy and Data Management">
  <div class="container">
    <a href="/" class="back">‚Üê Back to Home</a>
    
    <h1>üîí XAOSTECH Privacy & Data Management</h1>
    
    <div class="section">
      <h2>Privacy First</h2>
      <p>XAOSTECH uses first-party cookies only.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>functional</strong> - Account management, authorisation, cache and preferences</li>
        <li><strong><s>analytics</s></strong> - None + Cloudflare webbeacon disabled</li>
        <li><strong><s>marketing</s></strong> - None; not interested.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>Your Rights (GDPR)</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>‚úÖ <strong>Access:</strong> View your data at <a href="https://account.xaostech.io/profile">account.xaostech.io/profile</a></li>
        <li>‚úÖ <strong>Withdraw:</strong> Manage consent at <a href="https://data.xaostech.io">data.xaostech.io</a></li>
        <li>‚úÖ <strong>Delete:</strong> Request account deletion from your profile settings</li>
        <li>‚úÖ <strong>Export:</strong> Download your data package from account settings</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>Data Storage</h2>
      <p>All data is stored on Cloudflare infrastructure (D1, KV, R2) in compliance with EU data protection regulations.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Databases:</strong> Cloudflare D1 (SQLite)</li>
        <li><strong>Sessions:</strong> Cloudflare KV (encrypted)</li>
        <li><strong>Media:</strong> Cloudflare R2 (10GB free tier per user)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>GitHub OAuth:</strong> For account authentication (optional)</li>
        <li><strong>Cloudflare:</strong> CDN, Workers, storage infrastructure</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We do not sell or share your data with advertisers.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section status">
      <p>‚úì GDPR Compliant ‚Ä¢ ‚úì SameSite=Strict ‚Ä¢ ‚úì Zero-Trust Architecture</p>
      <p>Contact: <a href="mailto:privacy@xaostech.io">privacy@xaostech.io</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

